lays atop the map, but also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the content that forms the base map.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Data source for "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOption":{"abstract":[{"text":"Options for ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference"},{"text":" objects.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOption","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOption","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOption","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoption","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","title":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conforming to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol that returns","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"instances of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", then add a computed shape source to an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object along with an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object. The vector style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the computed shape","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"source.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"title":"MLNShapeSource","abstract":[{"type":"r